    ╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║                    🔧 HOW KMS TECHNOLOGY WORKS                        ║
    ╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
    
    KMS (Key Management Service) is Microsoft's own volume activation technology
    designed for businesses with hundreds of computers [citation:5]. KMS Pico
    simply creates a local KMS server on your own machine, tricking Windows
    and Office into thinking they're connected to a legitimate corporate
    activation server.
    
    The process is completely reversible and doesn't modify any system files —
    it simply installs a genuine KMS product key and connects to the local
    emulated server. Your operating system remains 100% authentic with all
    updates and features fully intact [citation:2].

